{
  "name": "Caloric Recharge",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Akimichi.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>By spending any number of calories, you are able to regain hit points by forcibly converting them into healing energies.</p><p>For every Calorie spent this way, you regain 1d6 + Constitution modifier in hit points, up to a maximum of 10 calories spent. Once you have spent a total of 10 calories in this way casting this jutsu prior to completing a rest of any type, you must complete a rest before you can recast this jutsu in this way.</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, you instead regain 1d8 + your constitution modifier in hit points per Calorie. If this jutsu is cast at S- Rank, you instead regain 1d10 + your constitution modifier in hit points per Calorie</p>",
